  • Method Details

    • processEntity

      public void processEntity(Entity entity, WorldRegion region)
      Description copied from class: KeystoneFilter
      Ran for every entity the filter is modifying after KeystoneFilter.processRegion(WorldRegion). Use this for modifications that can be done on a per-entity basis. Be sure that this code is self-contained, as this will be ran on multiple threads for improved performance, and as such is subject to race conditions
      Overrides:
      processEntity in class KeystoneFilter
      Parameters:
      entity - The Entity that is being modified
      region - The WorldRegion that the entity is in
